  "text": "An important adjunctive aspect of minimally invasive surgery is the decrease of resource utilization. [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] Significantly decreased hospital stay is reported in all reports on minimally invasive valve surgery. More patients discharged to home as opposed to skilled nursing facilities reflect improved functional status after surgery.",
